content: Nominate candidates for Crain's Eight Over Eighty and Notables in Finance sections  Crain's Cleveland Business
description: The nomination deadlines are coming up for both editorial features: Monday, Feb. 14, for Eight Over Eighty, and the following Monday, Feb. 21, for Notables in Finance. The features will run in print and online in April.
